function Start()
	idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

	idAsaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_AsaByWater)
	idDawoodClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_DawoodByWater)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaClone) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idDawoodClone) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_LonelyWolf_02_00d, idQuestOwner, idDawoodClone, idAsaClone)
	end
	
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAsaClone, loc_WaterWalkTo, "NPC_Walk", false)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idAsaClone, 1.5)
	end


	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idDawoodClone) then
		Hydra.QActorWait(idDawoodClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idDawoodClone, loc_WaterWalkTo, "NPC_Walk", false)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idDawoodClone, 1.5)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, snoQuest)
	idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	idAsaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Kehj_Armor_01_AsaFollower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idAsaFollower)
		
		Hydra.QActorWait(idAsaFollower, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_LonelyWolf_02_02a, idQuestOwner, idAsaFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAsaFollower, loc_DungeonRunTo, "NPC_Walk_Fast", false)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idAsaFollower, conv_LonelyWolf_02_02a)
		
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idAsaFollower, 1.5)
	end
end
